{
  "texts": [
    "This data set is composed of 443,352 images of 754 identities collected using 12 cameras, under 12 weather conditions (e.g., cloudy and foggy), 8 different illuminations (e.g., afternoon and midnight) and 26 typical locations, such as beach, street, school and mall.",
    "Two further versions of GPR were generated: GPR+ (Xiang et al. 2021) and FineGPR (Xiang et al. 2023).",
    "The former contains more identities and images than GPR; the latter contains more fine-grained details, mostly attributes of pedestrian models such as upper-and lower-body clothing colours, hats and bags.",
    "WePerson (Li et al. 2021) has been built using GTAV.",
    "It is composed of 4 million bounding boxes of 1500 identities acquired by 560 cameras."
  ]
}